headline: Macquarie Climate Solutions Fund Q2 2025 Commentary
summary: For 2Q25, Macquarie Climate Solutions Fund Institutional Class shares had positive absolute performance, but underperformed the Fund's benchmark, the MSCI ACWI IMI.
